how to get ad credit? for clickbank affiliates

To receive ad credits as a ClickBank affiliate, you need to be part of our current promotion. Silver/gold affiliates will receive $500 in ad credits, while diamond/platinum affiliates will receive $2,000. An onboarding call with our Account Managers and business verification are required to receive these credits. You can schedule the call through this link: [NewsBreak Advertising Consultation](https://calendly.com/d/z4w-3t3-rkw/newsbreak-advertising-consultation).
